snippet.title: Best VGM 1298 - Valkyrie Profile - Epic Poem to Sacred Death
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation / PSP
Valkyrie Profile (1999)
Epic Poem to Sacred Death
Motoi Sakuraba
